Change Log
==========

Version 1.0 (roadmap)
---------------------
- Add tools (init.d script)
- Create user documentation (doc dir + website/wiki)
- Add queue implementation: database
- Add database logger

Version 0.8.5 (planned)
-----------------------
+ Fix setting IPC status & statistics
+ Move namespace example tasks to App
- Add example tasks
- Add tutorial
- Clean up pid & ipc resources
- Refactor status into executor
- Refactor statistics into queue
+ Fix unit tests


Version 0.8.4 (27-11-2011)
==========================
+ Refactor manager
    + Move queue class to the process class
    + Add process pid ID to the logger log method
+ Implement manager process
    + Same
    + Child
    + Parallel
+ Refactor AbstractClasses -> ObjectAbstract


Version 0.8.3 (30-10-2011)
--------------------------
+ Implement daemon status action
    + define (recursive) data structure of ipc segments
    + read multiple ipc adapter types 
+ Implement manager
    + Gearman
+ Implement manager timers
    + Refactor triggers to timers
    + Interval
    + Cron
+ Implement daemon monitoring action
+ Add tutorial tasks
    + Minimal
    + Advanced


Version 0.8.2 (26-10-2011)
--------------------------
+ Implement loading task components by config file
+ Implement running a single task
+ Implement IPC adapters
    + DataBase
